title: 24. Rockabye (feat. Sean Paul & Anne-Marie) - Clean Bandit
text: Listened non-stop for a weekend Biography Formed: 2009 in Cambridge, England Genre: Dance Years Active: '10s A British genre crossover group best known for the hit "Rather Be," Clean Bandit mash classical music and pop forms for an airy and dreamy yet driven sound that's like the chamber music version of house music. The group was formed by four core members -- Grace Chatto on cello, percussion, and vocals; Jack Patterson on bass, keys, piano, and vocals; Luke Patterson on drums; and Neil Amin-Smith on violin and piano -- who were also known as the Chatto Quartet. The classically trained string quartet...   Clean Bandit 1.
